items.title: Awesome Webaudio
items.content_text:
### Packages / Apps

*   [AudioMass](https://audiomass.co/) - free, open source, web-based Audio and Waveform Editor.
*   [Csound IDE](https://ide.csound.com/) - web IDE for [CSound programming language](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Csound).

### Obsolete / Community

*   [Web Audio Modules](https://www.webaudiomodules.org/) - synthesizers and audio effects processors for web browsers (both API and implementations).

items.title: Awesome Eslint
items.content_text:
### Plugins / Security

*   [no-secrets (‚≠ê151)](https://github.com/nickdeis/eslint-plugin-no-secrets) - An eslint plugin that detects potential secrets/credentials.
*   [no-unsanitized (‚≠ê238)](https://github.com/mozilla/eslint-plugin-no-unsanitized) - Checks for `innerHTML`, `outerHTML`, etc.
*   [Security (‚≠ê2.3k)](https://github.com/nodesecurity/eslint-plugin-security) - ESLint rules for Node Security.
*   [xss (‚≠ê68)](https://github.com/Rantanen/eslint-plugin-xss) - Tries to detect XSS issues in codebase before they end up in production.
